<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/54860444-wanting"><img alt="Wanting: The Power of Mimetic Desire in Everyday Life" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1615240502l/54860444._SX98_.jpg" />
